ds_cdwtriage.description: Issues are New and have no target release set
ds_cdwtriage.jql: project = JBDS AND status = New AND ("Target Release" is EMPTY OR "CDW release" in ("?"))

ds_lockdown.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ('4.2.1.Final')) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ('8.0.1.GA'))

ds_maint.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ('4.2.0.Final', '4.2.1.Final', '4.2.2.Final')) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ('8.0.0.GA', '8.0.1.GA', '8.0.2.GA', '8.0.3.GA')))

ds_master.description: Current project+versions for devstudio stream. (JBIDE-4.3.*, JBDS-9.*)
ds_master.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion > '4.3.0.Alpha1' and fixVersion <= '4.3.0.Final') OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion > '9.0.0.Alpha1' and fixVersion <= '9.0.0.GA'))

ds_mystuff.description: Issues assigned to current user or in a component lead by current user.

ds_needpmack.description: Product manager have not yet approved a jira with a target release
ds_needpmack.jql: "Target Release" is not EMPTY AND "CDW pm_ack" = "?" AND resolution = Unresolved

ds_next.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ('4.2.2.Final', '4.3.0.Alpha1')) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ('8.0.2.GA', '9.0.0.Alpha1'))
